# <%= current_page.data.title %>

Automatic device configuration of [MoJ DNS](dns.html). This service helps devices when connected at sites reach the internet.

## User needs

This allows Public internet connectivity for prison staff to enable modern devices

## Principles

Enable onsite support staff to manage local devices through an online portal.

## Tools

The DHCP service uses [ISC Kea](https://www.isc.org/kea/) containers running on the AWS ECS Fargate service.